name: Oh_Home_Tara_Bookcase
description: With a rustic, industrial design, the Tara bookcase will make a wonderful addition to your home décor. The metal frame features black, powder metal coating. Four wide shelves offer ample storage space for your books, magazines, movies, and more. X-shaped metal braces are attached to the back for added support. The simple industrial design, and  chic rustic style of the Tara Bookcase, are sure look good in any room in your home.Industrial design and styleFour shelvesSturdy, durable constructionAsh veneer top and shelvesBlack powder coated metalOverall dimensions: 25.98 inches wide x 15 inches deep x 54.02 inches highShelf Type: BookshelvesMaterial: MDF, Veneer, MetalStyle: Rustic, UrbanAssembly: Assembly RequiredFinish: Ash FinishColor: Black, BrownStyleRustic, UrbanMaterialMDF, Metal, VeneerFinishAsh FinishShelf TypeBookshelvesAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBlack, Brown
